author: James Wilkinson For Dailymail.Com
title: Mark Zuckerberg starts US-wide tour with visit to Alabama | Daily Mail Online
text: Mark Zuckerberg turns Forrest Gump: Facebook founder starts off his tour of America with a shrimping boat trip in the movie character's home of Bayou La Batre, Alabama The billionaire couple are travelling around America to see how people live They started in Mobile and Bayou La Batre in Alabama on a Southern road trip Zuckerberg met fishermen, oyster farmers worshipers and musicians He has denied that this is the first salvo in a potential presidential run His US voyage is reminiscent of Tom Hanks's character's coast-to-coast run
